ActCanada Post Corporation Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Public Works and Government Services as the Minister for the purposes of the Act
PrecisOrder (a) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2006-67 of February 6, 2006; and (b) designating the MINISTER OF PUBLIC WORKS AND GOVERNMENT SERVICES a member of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada, as the MINISTER for the purposes of the CANADA POST CORPORATION ACT, effective November 4, 2015.
